<html><head><title>Hunt</title></head> <body bgcolor="#000000" text="#FFFFFF" vlink = "#99cccc" link = "#99ccff"  topmargin=0leftmargin=0 ><TABLE border = "0" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="5"><TR><TD valign = middle align = left  height = 300 ><font size="+1">First, I don't like talking to non-combatants about it. people who onlylisten and have not "been there" can not ever "feel" and "smell" the place.I never knew that you could see your own fears before your own eyes, nor ifanyone had told me what it was to be afraid to the point of wanting toclose out your own account, I wouldn't/couldn't think on that scale. ButVietnam did <A HREF = "hunt3.html">just that</A>.</font> <p>JJoel Hunt Sr.</TD></TR></table></body></html>